# neurostack install + init demo
Output docs/screenshots/cli/install.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 700
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 60ms
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set WindowBarSize 40

Sleep 500ms
Type "npm install -g neurostack"
Sleep 1500ms
Enter
Sleep 3s

Enter
Type "neurostack install --mode lite"
Sleep 1500ms
Enter
Sleep 4s

Enter
Type "neurostack init /tmp/my-vault -p researcher"
Sleep 1500ms
Enter
Sleep 5s

Sleep 2s
